stimulusHtml: Which of the following is always printed as a result of executing this code segment?

features.html:
In the following code segment,  x  is a properly declared and initialized  boolean  variable and  y  is a properly declared and initialized  int  variable. 

boolean a = !x && y > 50000; 
boolean b = !(x || y <= 50000); 
boolean c = !x || y <= 50000; 
boolean d = !(x && y <= 50000); 

if (a == b)
{     
   System.out.println("First");
}
if (a == c)
{
   System.out.println("Second");
} 
if (b == c)
{
   System.out.println("Third");
} 
if (c == d)
{       
   System.out.println("Fourth");
}
